-- Up Migration
-- Issue #245 (epic #251). Replaces the placeholder geometric SVGs from
-- migrations 9000 + 15000 with real CC-licensed Phylopic silhouettes for
-- every seeded AZ bird family. Generated by scripts/curate-phylopic.mjs
-- on 2026-04-26 (curator run date) using the Phylopic API two-step recipe
-- (/nodes?filter_name → /images?filter_node) and an auto-pick heuristic
-- (license preference CC0 > CC-BY > CC-BY-SA, then alphabetic creator).
--
-- The SVG path data is stored unmodified — per CC BY-SA 3.0 §1, serving
-- the exact SVG bytes through the API does NOT trigger share-alike on the
-- rest of the codebase (Adaptation vs Collection distinction). Per-row
-- attribution (creator + license URL) is rendered by the AttributionModal
-- (#250). The full audit trail (every candidate the heuristic considered,
-- per family) lives at scripts/phylopic-picks.json.
--
-- Picks were auto-selected by heuristic, NOT human-curated. The picker
-- HTML at scripts/curate-phylopic-review.html supports a manual visual
-- pass at 24-28px (FamilyLegend / MapCanvas symbol layer scales) before
-- the version-one → main release.
--
-- Slot ordering: this seed migration depends on schema migration
-- 1700000016000_add_creator_to_family_silhouettes.sql (lexically smaller
-- → applied first by node-pg-migrate). Without that column the UPDATE
-- below errors with column "creator" does not exist.
--
-- After version-one → main merge that includes this migration, the
-- operator runs scripts/purge-silhouettes-cache.sh (introduced in #252)
-- as part of the production deploy runbook to purge the CDN cache for
-- /api/silhouettes so users see the real silhouettes immediately instead
-- of waiting for max-age=604800 to expire on stale browser caches.

